high_descs: Turn around and go to the fridge.
Grab the soapbottle out of the refrigerator.
Turn around to go to the far edge of the countertop between the two bar stools.
Place the soapbottle on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Get the SoapBottle out of the refrigerator and place it on the CounterTop next to the bar stools.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge on the left.
Pick up the soapbottle from the fridge.
Turn around and walk around the countertop to reach the countertop next to the chair.
Put the soapbottle on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put the SoapBottle on the CounterTop.

high_descs: Move left, go to the wall, then left again. Go to the wall, before you get there, cross back to the left. Go to the fridge.
Open the refrigerator, grab the soapbottle on the second level. Close the door.
Turn around and move to the wall, turn right, go forward, turn right. Move to the middle of the countertop. Turn right. Stand in the middle of the countertop. Turn left.
Release the soapbottle on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Look for a SoapBottle on the CounterTop.
